66
00:03:54,650 --> 00:03:55,820
for 3 minutes

67
00:03:55,910 --> 00:03:57,160
3 minutes?

68
00:03:57,700 --> 00:04:00,160
there was enough family here…

69
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,490
in igami to work it

70
00:04:01,830 --> 00:04:05,120
