00:05:12,150 --> 00:05:14,400
so old-fashioned

105
00:05:15,570 --> 00:05:17,360
how about your bus?

106
00:05:17,450 --> 00:05:21,200
soon… you kuwako?

107
00:05:21,280 --> 00:05:23,030
i stay another night

108
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:25,040
