00:12:48,770 --> 00:12:49,690
12,000

165
00:12:49,770 --> 00:12:52,110
12,000… mom…

166
00:12:52,230 --> 00:12:53,610
kotoko is back from school?

167
00:12:53,730 --> 00:12:55,690
she has a photo exhibition for school

168
00:12:55,780 --> 00:12:57,950
