00:14:02,010 --> 00:14:02,720
excuse me

199
00:14:02,720 --> 00:14:03,300
sorry

200
00:14:03,300 --> 00:14:03,850
welcome back

201
00:14:03,890 --> 00:14:04,640
hello

202
00:14:10,140 --> 00:14:11,900
