203
00:14:11,980 --> 00:14:14,770
12,600

204
00:14:16,110 --> 00:14:17,730
1 pen, 2 chopstick

205
00:14:17,820 --> 00:14:20,400
that's what feeds a family

206
00:14:20,700 --> 00:14:23,030
