207
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:25,240
a writer is a waste

208
00:14:25,330 --> 00:14:27,700
you started at 43

209
00:14:27,790 --> 00:14:31,620
father moved to izu at 48

210
00:14:31,710 --> 00:14:34,210
i became a writer at 43

211
00:14:34,710 --> 00:14:36,800
