229
00:15:17,090 --> 00:15:19,460
a photo competition at school

230
00:15:19,550 --> 00:15:22,130
we ordered food for her

231
00:15:23,550 --> 00:15:25,340
thank you

232
00:15:25,430 --> 00:15:27,600
that kid is stubborn

233
00:15:27,850 --> 00:15:31,060
