299
00:20:43,040 --> 00:20:44,870
could you help?

300
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:45,660
all right

301
00:20:45,750 --> 00:20:46,620
thank you

302
00:20:47,040 --> 00:20:48,670
he'll carry you

303
00:20:48,790 --> 00:20:50,420
she's light

304
00:20:50,540 --> 00:20:52,710
please

